{
  "texts": [
    "This study explores the capabilities and limitations of GAI, with a focus on how it can aid in developing critical thinking skills.",
    "Our examples highlight challenges that may arise when using GAI tools like ChatGPT in educational settings, particularly in chemistry.",
    "These challenges underscore the need for fostering critical analysis skills when interacting with such technologies, as ChatGPT may occasionally generate responses that require careful examination.",
    "Teachers can create classroom activities that encourage students to critically evaluate AI-generated responses.",
    "Such activities can help develop analytical skills and emphasize the importance of verifying information, which is essential in science education, including chemistry."
  ]
}